{"data":[{"id":560719689,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"41f45ccee4c163bc21eb88c4cc632cbb","url_token":"yufei-liao","name":"车到山前必有树","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/bce6baeb61f7718b7f06ad262bc22bc7_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/bce6baeb61f7718b7f06ad262bc22bc7_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/41f45ccee4c163bc21eb88c4cc632cbb","user_type":"people","headline":"上传头像这么麻烦的事情我都做了，居然还要我写简介？","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":363,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560719689","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9a55f6345f56417bb5a366a4de6fcd41_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545881776,"updated_time":1546161595,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":348,"comment_count":41,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e第三次更新，刚看到题主问如果不发证明会如何。我建议吧...真要这样，不管是不是营销，大家吃瓜完毕后记得去举报一波封号吧。否则以后类似的操作可能会层出不穷。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有，评论里面有问，是否有严格证明“初等方法无法证出哥猜”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个问题问得相当好！！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的回答是，没有，都是我瞎说的。初等方法确实有可能证出哥猜，你说的对，你说的有道理。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别问，问就是我错了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-55ac3401ab72b7b8ea38cf49e48f239b_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"583\" data-rawheight=\"474\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8bae759dc3ea0663617fa2775338f372_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"583\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-55ac3401ab72b7b8ea38cf49e48f239b_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='583'%20height='474'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"583\" data-rawheight=\"474\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8bae759dc3ea0663617fa2775338f372_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"583\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-55ac3401ab72b7b8ea38cf49e48f239b_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-55ac3401ab72b7b8ea38cf49e48f239b_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e又看了一下，原来题主是一名高中生。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eum，怎么说呢，突然就并不觉得好笑了。反而有点难过。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很多人不理解为什么稍有了解的人都要泼冷水。为什么不能相信高手在民间。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实是因为，你看不懂这些泼冷水的人的善意。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e告诉你世界上没那么多奇迹，告诉你哥猜不可能由初等数学得出结论，告诉你如果你前16年不是一个天才那第17年也不太可能成为一个天才，告诉你想要解决数学问题还是要踏实学习高等数学，这很残忍，但很真实。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个解决哥猜的人在中国诞生，你们知道这是多大的荣光吗？每一个学习数学的人，其实心底里比你们更期待，只是，现实就是现实。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我去，回答完才发现，原来题主是证明出来了，所以才问这个问题的哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望题主一定要接受清北的学位奖金奖项教授头衔博士生导师职位等，让清北沾一下阁下的光！！！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e若是有这样的一个人...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e保送？？想什么呢？？你就是想送个博士学位给人家，还得看人家愿不愿意接受呢...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明了哥德巴赫猜想，还只是高中生(大概17岁左右)，清北的前缀实在不是很够看。单凭这个成果，菲尔兹绝对跑不掉了。更别说院士这种琐碎的头衔了...在这些面前，清北算什么...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e清北的数学系教授们估计会轮番发邮件询问论文里没看懂的内容，甚至求见面求讲座请教一下这个创新性的理论(若是能证出来，基本可以肯定是有一套新的理论体系了)。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哈哈，题主这个问题真是太  可爱了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e皇帝是不是在用金锄头耕地呢...\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"第三次更新，刚看到题主问如果不发证明会如何。我建议吧...真要这样，不管是不是营销，大家吃瓜完毕后记得去举报一波封号吧。否则以后类似的操作可能会层出不穷。 还有，评论里面有问，是否有严格证明“初等方法无法证出哥猜”。这个问题问得相当好！！我的…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=15\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized